# Group Weather Reports
Submit a Severe Weather Report or retrieve all spotters' reports within the last 180 minutes.

## Submit Severe Report [/report/severe]
### Create Severe Report [POST]
+ Request (application/json)

        {
           "id": "APPLICATION-ID", // Spotter ID
           "report_type": "S", // S = severe, W = winter
           "stamp": "YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM:SS",
           "tornado": 0, // boolean, 0 = no, 1 = yes
           "funnelcloud": 0, // boolean, 0 = no, 1 = yes
           "wallcloud": 0, // boolean, 0 = no, 1 = yes
           "rotation": 0, // boolean, 0 = no, 1 = yes
           "hail": 0, // boolean, 0 = no, 1 = yes
           "wind": 0, // boolean, 0 = no, 1 = yes
           "flood": 0, // boolean, 0 = no, 1 = yes
           "flashflood": 0, // boolean, 0 = no, 1 = yes
           "other": 1, // boolean, 0 = no, 1 = yes
           "hailsize": 0, // inches
           "windspeed": 0, // miles per hour
           "windmeasure": 0, // 0 = estimated, 1 = exact
           "stamp_exact": 0, // boolean, 0 = no, 1 = yes
           "damage": 0, // boolean, 0 = no, 1 = yes
           "injury": 0, // boolean, 0 = no, 1 = yes
           "narrative": "test test test", // short narrative
           "lat": 39.763819, // latitude
           "lon": -105.2217393, // longitude
           "gps": 1, // boolean, 0 = no, 1 = yes
           "nwschat": 1, // submit to NWSChat
           "twitter": 1 // submit to Twitter (@SpotterNetwork)
        }


+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
        }

